description:
When our faith seems “lukewarm,” it can often be due to limited participation in evangelism.

However, owning a cellphone provides a simple opportunity for anyone to become a digital missionary.

On ANN Weekly, learn how Marius’ ignited his faith by using his cellphone to share the gospel.

Find this story and more on our website, adventist.news.
fulltitle: Digital Evangelism Ignites the Faith of a “Lukewarm” Adventist
